'''Base communications''' (basecom):  [[telecommunication|Communications]] services, such as the installation, [[operation]], [[repair and maintenance|maintenance]], augmentation, modification, and rehabilitation of communications networks, systems, facilities, and equipment, including off-post extensions, provided for the operation of a military post, camp, installation, station, or activity. ''Synonym'' '''communications [[base station]]'''.

Source: from [[Federal Standard 1037C]]

